headline: American Tower Plans Second Quarter 2025 Earnings Release and Conference Call
summary: BOSTON, July 07, 2025--American Tower Corporation (NYSE: AMT) announced today that the press announcement of its second quarter 2025 results is scheduled to be released to the news services at 7:00 a.m. ET on Tuesday, July 29, 2025. In addition, the Company has scheduled a conference call at 8:30 a.m. ET on July 29, 2025, to discuss its results.

headline: W.P. Carey Stock Rises 16% Year to Date: Will the Trend Last?
summary: WPC stock jumps 16% YTD, driven by dividend growth, rent escalations and strategic asset shifts.
